Пусть \(5^{x} =t\), тогда:
$$t+\frac{125}{t-126}\geq 0\\ \frac{t^2-126t+125}{t-126} \geq 0\\ \frac{( t-125)( t-1)}{t-126} \geq 0$$
$$\displaystyle \left[ \begin{array}{l l}
\begin{cases}
t\geq 1\\
t\leq 125
\end{cases}\\
\ \ t >126
\end{array} \right. \Rightarrow \left[ \begin{array}{l l}
\begin{cases}
5^{x} \geq 5^{0}\\
5^{x} \leq 5^{3}
\end{cases}\\
\ 5^{x} >126
\end{array} \right. \Rightarrow \left[ \begin{array}{l l}
\ \ \ \begin{cases}
x\geq 0\\
x\leq 3
\end{cases}\\
x >\log_{5} 126
\end{array} \right.$$
Ответ: \([0;3]\cup ( \log_5⁡126;+\infty )\).
